com.etouch.amazon.listener

Class SuiteListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.etouch.amazon.listener.SuiteListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.testng.ISuiteListener, org.testng.ITestNGListener

    public class SuiteListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.testng.ISuiteListener
    The listener interface for receiving suite events. The class that is interested in processing a suite event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addSuiteListener method. When the suite event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
    Author:
    eTouch Systems Corporation
